---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about HonestPickReview's mission to provide independent, research-driven product reviews.">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 24px;">
    <p class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / About</p>
  </div>
  <article class="container prose" style="max-width: 720px; padding-bottom: 48px;">
    <h1>About HonestPickReview</h1>
    <p>
      HonestPickReview was created to cut through marketing noise and give shoppers a clear, research-driven
      view of everyday physical products — from kitchen appliances to power tools to baby gear.
    </p>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      We believe good buying decisions come from comparing real specifications, understanding trade-offs, and
      looking past a single glowing (or scathing) review. Our goal is to save you the hours of research it
      would otherwise take to feel confident about a purchase.
    </p>
    <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
    <p>
      Our rankings and recommendations are based on our own research process, described in detail on our
      <a href="/how-we-review/">How We Review</a> page. Some links on this site are affiliate links — see our
      <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details — but affiliate relationships never
      determine which products we recommend or how we rate them.
    </p>
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>Have a correction, suggestion, or product you'd like us to cover? <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
